  #link("https://sumnerevans.com../../travel/2022-berlin-matrix-summit/summit/index.md")[Matrix Community Summit]
  and got to meet some awesome people and make new friends.
- The opportunity to give my
  #link("https://sumnerevans.com../../../portfolio#presentation-hungryserv")[first]
  #link("https://sumnerevans.com../../../portfolio#presentation-what-is-beeper-working-on")[ever]
  #link("https://sumnerevans.com../../../portfolio#presentation-matrix-bot-workshop")[presentations]
