- Getting to travel to see
  #link("https://sumnerevans.com../../travel/2022-oakland-california/index.md")[multiple]
  #link("https://sumnerevans.com../../travel/2022-starbase-texas/index.md")[friends].
- My vacation in
  #link("/categories/trip-to-portugal-and-france")[Lisbon and Paris], and all of the
